PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775844664
OL,3,CCouncil faces legal action over
OL,4,Cdecision on Oxford United's new stadium
OL,6,FA campaign group, Friends of
OL,7,FStratfield Brake, has questioned
OL,8,Fwhether the council properly
OL,9,Fconsidered advice from Natural England
OL,10,Fover the environmental effects on a
OL,11,Fneighbouring woodland.
OL,13,FNatural England recommended a
OL,14,Fprecautionary approach because it is
OL,15,Finconclusive as to whether the
OL,16,Fwoodland is ancient, according to the
OL,17,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
