PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775844664
OL,3,CCouncil faces legal action over
OL,4,Cdecision on Oxford United's new stadium
OL,6,FA challenge has also been made against
OL,7,Fthe council's assessment of matchday
OL,8,Froad closures, saying there is no
OL,9,Fevidential basis for the authority to
OL,10,Fassume that measures can be set up and
OL,11,Fremoved quickly.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
