PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775844664
OL,3,CCouncil faces legal action over
OL,4,Cdecision on Oxford United's new stadium
OL,6,FLaw firm Leigh Day, which is
OL,7,Frepresenting the group, has filed a
OL,8,Flegal claim at the High Court and will
OL,9,Fseek to persuade a judge to quash the
OL,10,Fplanning permission decision.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the group said: "We
OL,13,Fhave engaged with the council
OL,14,Fthroughout this process and made our
OL,15,Fconcerns clear at every stage,
OL,16,Fincluding through formal legal
OL,17,Fcorrespondence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775844664
OL,3,CCouncil faces legal action over
OL,4,Cdecision on Oxford United's new stadium
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, those concerns have
OL,7,Fnot been addressed, leaving us with no
OL,8,Foption but to bring this judicial
OL,9,Freview.
OL,11,F"We believe the decision is flawed and
OL,12,Fthat the impacts of this development
OL,13,Fon the adjacent woodland and transport
OL,14,Fhave not been properly considered."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
