PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775844664
OL,3,CCouncil faces legal action over
OL,4,Cdecision on Oxford United's new stadium
OL,6,FLeigh Day partner Ricardo Gama said:
OL,7,F"Our clients felt they had no choice
OL,8,Fbut to file court proceedings because
OL,9,Fthe council has failed to address
OL,10,Ftheir concerns over the impact which
OL,11,Fthe stadium development would have on
OL,12,Fan ecologically important woodland and
OL,13,Fon local traffic.
OL,15,F"They look forward to putting their
OL,16,Farguments to a judge."
OL,18,FCherwell District Council has been
OL,19,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
